Package org.omg.CosNaming.NamingContextPackage Description

This package contains Exception classes for the org.omg.CosNaming package. The list of exception classes are:

  • AlreadyBound
  • CannotProceed
  • InvalidName
  • NotEmpty
  • NotFound
  • NotFoundReason
